Here I have updated the CBT #638 package with following enhancements:

1. Add support Mail 'FROM:' statement in SYSIN DD.
2. Get the system hostname and domain name automatically.
3. Add web link for the attachment file in email body.
4. Enhance the MIME support, including:
    Encode the email body to avoid the possible '.' command.
    Use single boundary
    Automatic recognize application for MIME file types
5. Enhancement for attachments:
    Support DDNAME in Dataset Name field.
6. Enhancement for encoding program:
    Support different input and output DD name via EXEC PARM.
7. Remove the record length restriction of SYSIN DD.

        October 5, 2004

